Good!  I know exactly what I'm going to throw every turn!  
Can you win a perfect round of 20 throws by round 40?

My throws are random but I'll give you some time to figure it out.  I'll even tell you how many throws you got right the previous round!  Helpful as always I am!  I even gave you a template to keep track of your wins.

You just need to guess what I am throwing by returning your guess to me in an int[] array.


```csharp

